{"title":"请坐吧，不要谢我","authors":["胡丰传"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":12,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"请坐吧，不要谢我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡丰传"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在拥挤的公共汽车上，我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给一位年轻的孕妇让座。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她望望我，蓦地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸上泛起一层红的羞涩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大概是因为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看我年岁轻轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸上还有腼腆与羞涩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢过我，她终于坐下了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若不坐下，座位只好空着……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我对她说，不必谢我！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是个共青团员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象初升的太阳，正熊熊地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧着生命之火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然，祖国是个大家庭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家庭里的人难道不应"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我关心你，你体贴我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共唱一支优美和谐的歌？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}